Hello, John.

832
01:40:21,821 --> 01:40:25,155
你好，約翰
John, hello.

833
01:40:29,996 --> 01:40:32,950
你的靈魂
You're the one soul. . .

834
01:40:33,333 --> 01:40:36,951
我是一定要親自來收的
. . .l would come up here
to collect myself.

835
01:40:40,298 --> 01:40:42,670
我听說了
So l've heard.

836
01:40:43,426 --> 01:40:44,754
不介意吧？
You mind?

837
01:40:45,803 --> 01:40:48,176
哦，可以，隨意
我有時間
Oh, go-- Go right ahead. l've got stock.

838
01:40:49,182 --> 01:40:50,593
