Coffin nail.

839
01:40:51,100 --> 01:40:52,974
和你很配，約翰
Very fitting, John.

840
01:40:55,855 --> 01:40:59,390
知道嗎，割得太深會割斷肌腱
You know, when you cut too deep,
you cut the tendons. . .

841
01:40:59,567 --> 01:41:02,354
手指就不听使喚了
. . .finger movement goes
out the window.

842
01:41:02,528 --> 01:41:04,604
我來幫你
Let me help you.

843
