Boys will be boys.

856
01:42:04,424 --> 01:42:05,752
和加百列在一起
With Gabriel.

857
01:42:08,594 --> 01:42:11,382
有些愛好真的沒法解釋
No accounting for taste, really.

858
01:42:11,764 --> 01:42:14,172
他們拿著命運之矛
They have the Spear of Destiny.

859
01:42:16,936 --> 01:42:20,637
“他們拿著命運之矛”
''They have the Spear of Destiny. ''

860
01:42:28,948 --> 01:42:32,151
又想和我玩什么花樣？
Or is it another one of your cons?

861
