Son of perdition.

868
01:44:08,256 --> 01:44:09,584
小喇叭
Little horn.

869
01:44:11,718 --> 01:44:13,924
最邪惡的人
Most unclean.

870
01:44:14,095 --> 01:44:16,716
真怀念這些舊時的稱呼
l do miss the old names.

871
01:44:17,598 --> 01:44:19,805
該回家了，儿子
Time to go home, son.

872
01:44:19,976 --> 01:44:22,431
我要替上帝
l will smite thee. . .

873
01:44:22,603 --> 01:44:25,521
懲罰你
. . .in his honor.

874
