好像某人不再支持你了
Looks like somebody doesn't
have your back anymore.

875
01:44:53,593 --> 01:44:55,420
父親？
Father?

876
01:45:18,826 --> 01:45:20,237
那么
So.

877
01:45:27,251 --> 01:45:28,580
那么什么
So.

878
01:45:28,961 --> 01:45:32,710
好了，你想要什么？
再給你延期？
Yeah, what do you want? An extension?

879
01:45:37,470 --> 01:45:39,463
她的妹妹
The sister. . .

880
01:45:40,390 --> 01:45:41,718
