讓她回家
Let her go home.

883
01:45:52,694 --> 01:45:57,272
你愿意放棄你的生命
讓她升入天堂？
You're willing to give up your life
so she can go to heaven?

884
01:46:07,083 --> 01:46:10,119
好的，可以
Fine. lt's done.

885
01:46:12,755 --> 01:46:16,207
