. . .the chance to prove. . .

893
01:48:07,954 --> 01:48:13,328
你的靈魂是屬于地獄的
. . .that your soul truly belongs in hell.

894
01:48:16,379 --> 01:48:19,463
哦，你要活著
Oh, you will live.

895
01:48:23,803 --> 01:48:27,670
你要活著
You will live.

896
