Hide it.

923
01:52:13,533 --> 01:52:16,569
藏在一個沒人能找到的地方
Somewhere no one
will ever be able to find it.

924
01:52:17,620 --> 01:52:19,280
包括我
Not even me.

925
01:52:23,459 --> 01:52:25,251
就知道沒那么簡單
Always a catch.

926
01:52:26,713 --> 01:52:28,290
